'''前體B細胞淋巴細胞白血病'''({{lang|en|Precursor B-cell lymphoblastic leukemia}})是[[淋巴白血病|淋巴白血病]](Lymphoid leukemia)的一種形式，大多數的[[B细胞|B细胞]][[淋巴母細胞|淋巴母細胞]](Lymphoblast、未成熟的白血球)被發現在[[血液|血液]]和[[骨髓|骨髓]]中。它也是最常見類型的[[急性淋巴性白血病|急性淋巴性白血病]](ALL)。它有時被歸類為"淋巴瘤"(lymphoma)，如所指稱的"白血病/淋巴瘤"(leukemia/lymphoma)。

==子類型==
它包括以下的子類型：<ref>{{cite journal |author=Randolph TR |title=Advances in acute lymphoblastic leukemia |journal=Clin Lab Sci |volume=17 |issue=4 |pages=235–45 |year=2004 |pmid=15559730 |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qa3890/is_200410/ai_n9429273/pg_2 |access-date=2014-04-10 |archive-date=2009-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090823023159/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qa3890/is_200410/ai_n9429273/pg_2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* t(9;22)-BCR/ ABL
* t(v;11q23)-MLL 重排
* t(1;19)-E2A/PBX1
* t(12;21)-ETV/ CBFα
* [http://atlasgeneticsoncology.org/Anomalies/t1719ID1078.html t(17;19)-E2A-HLF] {{Wayback|url=http://atlasgeneticsoncology.org/Anomalies/t1719ID1078.html |date=20120726033834 }}

==分子機制==
一個有趣的模型"前體B細胞急性淋巴性白血病"(B-cell ALL)顯示了單一基因的功能異常，即PAX5，它能夠改變"B細胞表型"(phenotype of B cell)至"前體細胞"(precursor cell)。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Carotta S, Nutt SL |title=Losing B cell identity |journal=BioEssays |volume=30 |issue=3 |pages=203–7 |date=March 2008 |pmid=18293359 |doi=10.1002/bies.20725 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Den Boer ML, van Slegtenhorst M, De Menezes RX, ''et al.'' |title=A subtype of childhood acute lymphoblastic leukaemia with poor treatment outcome: a genome-wide classification study |journal=Lancet Oncol. |volume=10 |issue=2 |pages=125–34 |date=February 2009 |pmid=19138562 |pmc=2707020 |doi=10.1016/S1470-2045(08)70339-5 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1470-2045(08)70339-5 |access-date=2014-04-10 |archive-date=2022-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220201194112/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1470-2045(08)70339-5 }}</ref>

